Read Memory Page command

Parameters:
requestFlags - byte with flags
pageNumber - number of page, which should be read
result - FedmIscTagHandler_Maxim_Result object containing return values
Returns:
operation status

Description:
Command execution realized with [0xBF] ISO 15693 Transparent command

The return value status indicates the success:
0 - tramsmission was successful
status byte (>1), if the reader signals a problem
error code (<0), if something goes wrong
The result object of type FedmIscTagHandler_Maxim_Result contains only valid data, if the operation status is 0.
